{
  "stem": "5188.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When we had our health examination-- and this is at the American consulate-- they discovered that I couldn't see as well as I should be seeing, and that I couldn't come to the United States unless I had glasses.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Here we were in Stuttgart, which was probably the biggest trip I had ever taken at that point, because it was in southern Germany, and that was the nearest place for an American consulate.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I needed glasses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well, no kid ever got glasses as fast as I did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This was in the morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My parents took me out into the city somewhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We saw an optometrist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I don't know, but I got glasses within an hour or two.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we went back to the consulate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they gave us-- gave me my visa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that was the big excitement in Stuttgart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we all had a visa to come to the United States now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And it was time to make arrangements to really leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we did that relatively quickly, considering that we got the visa in December-- on my passport, it's stamped December the 6th-- we very quickly put our house on the market.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I must say, the store was open again, so we had a business to sell.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And somebody local bought our house with the business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a Jewish, a Christian family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And not only that, they also bought a piece of property that we had, like a meadow, down by the river, just a piece of land.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we sold that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they paid us, but then we couldn't take the money out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what we did, my parents bought a lot of stuff.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They really spent money like they never did in their life.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
